title: Girls Gotta Eat
description:
Girls Gotta Eat Rayna Greenberg and Ashley Hesseltine are talking all things sex! They share their hook up philosophies and awkward sex stories, breakdown the dating apps, discuss the whole social media DM thing, and give Lala some real world advice about sex and dating! Rayna and Ashley drop the 411 on how they met and started their pod, why New York is not a good city for dating or meeting people, and when a one-night stand can be more! Plus, Lala dishes on losing her virginity, exploring her own sexual anatomy right down to a taste test, and the meaning of #UpInTheNight.
